Description: Swordsmen are warriors who have strong physical abilities.{nl}They use various weapons to deal with enemies up close{nl}and stand at the front lines.
Name: Swordsman

Description: Highlanders are tough fighters who use two-handed swords. They make enemies collide against each other or against terrain, so they are great for handling multiple enemies.
Name: Highlander

Description: Peltastas are defensive warriors who use shields to block enemy attacks and provoke enemies.
Name: Peltasta

Description: Hoplites use spears with a long attack range. They gain a bonus when fighting against strong, large-sized enemies.
Name: Hoplite

Description: Centurions command the battle with formations. They control their allies and use different formations depending on the situation.
Name: Centurion

Description: Barbarians are reckless and aggressive warriors who are not bound to the rules of battle, and would do anything to ensure victory.
Name: Barbarian

Description: Cataphracts use two-handed spears. They act as cavalry who break through and scatter enemy formations.
Name: Cataphract

Description: Corsairs are specialized in dual-wielding and ambushing enemies from behind. Anyone who joins a Corsair's party becomes a pirate.
Name: Corsair

Description: Doppelsoeldners are mercenaries who endure high risk for high rewards. They dangerously expose themselves to enemies to receive high attack power or high EXP.
Name: Doppelsoeldner

Description: Rodeleros ambush and demolish enemies. Their defensive skills using shields are effective for blocking long range attacks.
Name: Rodelero

Description: Squires are warriors who support their allies. They support by repairing and enhancing others' weapons, or by setting up a base camp to aid their team.
Name: Squire

Description: The Murmillo is a gladiatorial class that has a fine balance between offense and defense. It is capable of wearing a Cassis Crista to block ranged attacks or to enhance any shield related skills.
Name: Murmillo

Description: Shinobis are warriors who are familiar with special tactics called Ninjutsu. Only few can overcome the long and harsh training required to become a Shinobi.
Name: Shinobi

Description: The Fencer class makes use of the Rapier weapon to rapidly hit successive strikes on their enemy.
Name: Fencer

Description: Dragoons are elite warriors who are specialized in using spears for battle. They benefit from using two-handed spears.
Name: Dragoon

Description: Templars are commanding leaders who organize guilds and lead those within their guild. Only a Templar can become a guild master and determine the outcome of his or her guild.
Name: Templar

Description: The Lancer is a cavalry class that uses strong anti-personnel skills. It is capable of charging through enemy magic circles and obstacles.
Name: Lancer

Description: The Matador is a bullfighter who strongly provokes enemies and is specialized in swift movement for attacking and retreating.{nl}Interact with the Matador Notice Board in Orsha then speak with Litis, Naglis, and Linas in Escanciu Village. Afterwards, meet with the Matador Master in Fedimian.
Name: Matador

Description: Nak Muay is a class that makes use of close-range, physical attack Muay Thai techniques. The efficacy and amount of their combat effects rely mostly on strength.
Name: Nak Muay

Description: The Retiarii are gladiators who use the net (or 'rete'), one-handed spear and dagger as their main weapons in combat. This class is specialized in using the rete to entrap or disarm their opponents.{nl}Meet their Master at Tenants' Farm.
Name: Retiarius

Description: Wizards use magic to block attacks and protect themselves.{nl}They can cast powerful and concentrated spells, dealing damage to a single target or multiple enemies in an area.
Name: Wizard

Description: Pyromancers use successive fire magic to fight against multiple enemies.
Name: Pyromancer

Description: Cryomancers use powerful ice magic to freeze enemies, or protect their allies from enemies by using ice walls.
Name: Cryomancer

Description: Psychokinos use psychokinesis to control gravity, or pull enemies and throw them around.
Name: Psychokino

Description: Alchemists use alchemy to enhance gems and synthesize or craft items.
Name: Alchemist

Description: Sorcerers summon and control spirits to fight enemies, or even to use as mounts.
Name: Sorcerer

Description: Linkers link allies together to reduce incoming damage, or connect enemies to amplify the inflicted damage.
Name: Linker

Description: Chronomancers are wizards who control time. They stop, speed up, or change back time to help allies.
Name: Chronomancer

Description: Necromancers are wizards who utilize magic involving the dead. They attack with, or create summoned creatures, using corpses collected over time.
Name: Necromancer

Description: Thaumaturges use magic that change the attributes and sizes of targets. They can shrink enemies or strengthen allies to aid them in battle.
Name: Thaumaturge

Description: Elementalists harness the elements and can cast powerful magic attacks. However, their spells have a long cooldown time, so it is recommended to cooperate with other players.
Name: Elementalist

Description: Mimic
Name: Mimic

Description: Taoist Dummy
Name: Citydummy

Description: The Sage is a class that is able to manipulate space by learning about the basics of how the world is constructed. It is capable of using dimension manipulating magic or portals to move where it pleases.
Name: Sage

Description: Warlocks are wizards who harness the power of evil spirits. They can summon evil spirits and can command them to defeat monsters.
Name: Warlock

Description: Featherfoots are wizards who utilize the power of incantations. They can absorb an enemy's life, or help allies by making enemies weak from a curse.
Name: Featherfoot

Description: Rune Casters are wizards who use ancient symbols imbued with magic. Although it takes some time to draw energy from the symbols, they contain enormous power.
Name: Rune Caster

Description: The Enchanter class is able to help allies by crafting consumable items or enhancing equipment.
Name: Enchanter

Description: The Shadowmancer is a mage that is able to perform powerful attacks or hide in the shadows.{nl}Start by talking with the shadow that has appeared in Library Annex Roof at Taniel I Avenue.
Name: Shadowmancer

Description: The Onmyoji are able to summon divine spirits and use the magic of Yin and Yang in combat, which allows them to face a large number of opponents simultaneously.{nl}To meet their Master, speak to Uska in Klaipeda.
Name: Onmyoji

Description: Archers use bows and various secondary equipment.{nl}Their specialties are long-ranged and agile attacks.
Name: Archer

Description: Hunters are trainers who hunt enemies using companions. Companions use skills which require cooperation with their owners, such as biting and holding onto enemies, or finding hidden targets.
Name: Hunter

Description: Quarrel Shooters use a crossbow and shield for strategic combat. They can defend against long-range attacks using their pavises, placing them in the ground.
Name: Quarrel Shooter

Description: Rangers specialize in fighting against multiple enemies with their quick and long-range attacks.
Name: Ranger

Description: Sappers are archers who build traps and lure enemies into them.
Name: Sapper

Description: A Wugushi specialize in using various poisons to attack or bewitch enemies.
Name: Wugushi

Description: The Hackapell is a cavalry class that uses both ranged and melee weapons. It has high movement capabilities and various combinations skills using melee and ranged weapons.
Name: Hackapell

Description: Scouts specialize in reconnaissance and infiltration. They use stealth to hide themselves and convey the enemy's situation to allies, providing an advantage in battle.
Name: Scout

Description: Rogues are combat professionals who will do anything for victory. They're specialized at ambushing enemies from behind using bows and daggers.
Name: Rogue

Description: Schwarzer Reiters maneuver quickly. They specialize in diverse shooting techniques using a pistol.
Name: Schwarzer Reiter

Description: Fletchers make and use special arrows. Different arrows result in powerful attacks depending on the type of enemy and combat situation.
Name: Fletcher

Description: Pied Pipers play the flute to control enemies or create beneficial effects for their allies.{nl}Start by talking to Item Merchant Muras in Fedimian and tell him that he looks worried.
Name: Pied Piper

Description: Appraisers are a class that can identify unidentified items. In combat, Appraisers use their skills to evaluate both allies and enemies.
Name: Appraiser

Description: Falconers control Hawks. Hawks may be fussy, but they become reliable companions when trained well.
Name: Falconer

Description: Cannoneers are archers who use powerful cannons to deal massive damage from above, or blast flying enemies from below.
Name: Cannoneer

Description: Musketeers are equipped with rifles. Even though they cannot use a bow at the same time, they have effective skills for continuous hits and close combat techniques.
Name: Musketeer

Description: The Mergen is a class that uses large bows and is most effective when facing numerous enemies.
Name: Mergen

Description: The Bullet Marker is an archer that uses bullets have various properties or effects.{nl}You can meet their Master after talking to Manager Rota several times.
Name: Bullet Marker

Description: Clerics heal and protect allies through the blessings{nl}of the goddess, while knocking down their enemies {nl}with powerful blows.
Name: Cleric

Description: Priests are clerics who give blessings and resurrect the dead with their holy powers.
Name: Priest

Description: Krivis are priests who use divine fire to help allies recover or to deal massive damage to enemies.
Name: Krivis

Description: Bokors use voodoo skills to raise the dead or curse their enemies to attack them from afar.
Name: Bokor

Description: Druids are clerics who use the power of nature. They control plants to help allies, or transform into monsters to use that monster's abilities.
Name: Druid

Description: A Sadhu can use their soul to assault enemies with unseen attacks or convey their powers to other players.
Name: Sadhu

Description: Dievdirbys can carve and place sacred statues. Their statues can protect allies or attack enemies.
Name: Dievdirbys

Description: Oracles are clerics who possess foresight. They can predict or interfere with an enemy's attacks and determine their fate.
Name: Oracle

Description: Monks are clerics who train in martial arts through the blessing of the goddess.
Name: Monk

Description: Pardoners are clerics who don't shy from increasing their wealth through the goddess' blessing.
Name: Pardoner

Description: Paladins use their holy power to protect allies and vanquish enemies through the blessings of the goddess.
Name: Paladin

Description: The Chaplain is an army based class that uses divine power to aid allies in combat. Only advanced priests at a high level can become a Chaplain.
Name: Chaplain

Description: Shepherd
Name: Shepherd

Description: Plague Doctors are priests who can heal the status ailments of allies, or incinerate an enemy with a status ailment. Their special Bird Beak Mask has a special drug to block status ailments.
Name: Plague Doctor

Description: Kabbalists are priests who practice an ancient magic known as Kabbalah. They can support allies by using infinite power, or attack by using a defense formation to disintegrate the enemy's name.
Name: Kabbalist

Description: The Inquisitor is a class that judges those that are defying the goddesses. It has strong offensive techniques and is specialized in combat against magic users.
Name: Inquisitor

Description: The Taoist class uses the power of Taoism. It is capable of using a talisman to attack enemies or help allies.
Name: Taoist

Description: Mikos receive the prophecy and serve the goddesses. They attack enemies with Holy property attacks or give buffs to the allies by raising their spirits up.
Name: Miko

Description: The Zealot is specialized in enhancing oneself through the use of buffs for physical melee attacks.{nl}Find the hidden tombstone in Vera Coast if you're looking into this class.
Name: Zealot

Description: Exorcists use magic of divine properties to expel evil energies and overthrow demonic enemies.{nl}Start by meeting the Exorcist in Fedimian.
Name: Exorcist

Description: GM
Name: GM
